"content": "<h2>A garment worn by priests and high priests</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:4\">EXO 28:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:6-Exod28:13\">EXO 28:6–28:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:2-Exod39:7\">EXO 39:2–39:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:7\">LEV 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:5\">JDG 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:17-Judg18:20\">JDG 18:17–18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:28\">1SA 2:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:18\">1SA 22:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:9\">1SA 23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:4\">HOS 3:4</a></p>\n<h2>Worn by people other than priests</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:14\">2SA 6:14</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:27\">1CH 15:27</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:27\">JDG 8:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:18\">1SA 2:18</a></p>",
